sivappu mazhai ( tamil : சிவப்பு மழை ; english : ( lit . ) red rain ) is a 2010 tamil action film written and directed by v. krishnamurthy .   earlier referred to as guinness vision , the film was made in 11 days 23 hours 45 minutes , breaking the guinness world record .   the film features the tamil canadian multiple guinness world record-holder suresh joachim , who produced the film , in the lead role , whilst meera jasmine , vivek and suman play other prominent roles .